
200g chocolate
4 eggs
350g sugar
1.75dl oil
175g flour
1 tsp baking powder
half tsp salt
half vanilla pod
100g hazelnut (70 ground, in it, 30 rough on top)

* melt chocolate with the oil on double boiler
* beat eggs and sugar until foamy, add melted chocolate
* add flour, baking powder, salt, hazelnut, vanilla and mix until homogenous
* bake at 150-170c for 30 min in ~40x28, 3cm tall sheet
